Baraawe, like much of Somalia, has had lots of violence. In September 2009, the United States launched an air attack that killed 4 people, including terrorist Saleh Ali Saleh Naban.

Currently, you should not travel to Baraawe, let alone Somalia. Baraawe is extremely dangerous, and you most certainly risk your life if you travel by yourself. Even with an armed guard, you could still be targeted.
